nodes.text: The Coruscant Holo Net: Chancellor Safe

The Coruscant Holo Net: Chancellor Safe was an in-universe issue of The Coruscant Holo Net that was published in Star Wars Comic 4. It extrapolated on events featured in the comic story Too Many Cooks.

Although it was published in 23 BBY, this issue of The Coruscant Holo Net contains an advertisement featuring a clone trooper and droid tri-fighters. It also contains another advertisement which mistakenly states that Naboo is in the Outer Rim Territories.
